C ya, Logo!

::Prowl/Ramulus::

"My name's Prowl," Prowl tells Bluestreak, "Who are y-" he's interruped by 
Brooder and co. landing. He groans. Was there never any peace?

He walks out of the Ark and looks at Brooder. "Hello," he says cautioustly, 
hand near his gun, "I am Prowl. May I ask who you are and what you are doing 
here?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus nods. "The ship already landed," he says, taking off at a gallop for 
Africa (which is where the ship landed).
